{"tid":310575,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（開戰了）美國提對北韓動武決議案 遭中國、俄羅斯反對","createTime":"2017-07-06T02:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T02:31:10.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51bf4db7f605a7db2f4f0739911ce162da882931","tid":310575,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:23:31.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕北韓4日宣布成功試射其第一枚洲際彈道飛彈（ICBM），更宣稱飛彈能夠攜帶大型核彈頭。美國駐聯合國大使海利（Nikki Haley）警告，如果有必要，會動用武力阻止北韓的核子飛彈計畫。<br />\n海利今日表示，北韓試射洲際飛彈是明顯及急劇的軍事升級，使外交途徑解決北韓問題的機會迅速降低，美國準備使用一切能力捍衛自己和盟友。<br />\n海利指出，美方將在未來幾天內提出對北韓的新制裁建議，並警告中國和其他支持北韓的國家，如果他們不停止幫助金正恩政權，美國可能會停止與他們的貿易。法國也呼籲聯合國採納新的決議案，加強對北韓的制裁，但中國和俄羅斯都反對向北韓動武。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2122780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2122780&d=HXK%2BZLsE%2FC8stDE2Q2TB%2BJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=f2e1d3c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2122780&h=decff778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2122780</a><br />\n美國可能又不的理聯合國反對開拖"},{"pid":"b7888f87058800d9d9a2a81333fa94d30877b667","tid":310575,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"侵侵加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082fa339aa6682cd6d46e20428a9351dc48294cd","tid":310575,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:29:16.000Z","msg":"邊撚到提動武呀死標題黨"},{"pid":"0842bcbb25b85ca9b15a555807d1fd3347745c12","tid":310575,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:30:45.000Z","msg":"侵仔好波"},{"pid":"b6175a979c30f14f95e691640ee96fdcc9183e79","tid":310575,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:31:10.000Z","msg":"支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}